item.title: By: Kevin Pettitt
item.dc:creator: Kevin Pettitt
item.description: <p>I think the fact that you're pretty high on a pretty long list is a testament to the power of regular blogging. Prior to starting my blog 2 months ago I was about even with Kevin Pettitt the race car driver, who gets written up regularly on racing news sites. I just checked and I have the 1 thru 9 positions locked up, with my racing friend making only a token showing at #10. Guess that's why they call it ego surfing <img src="<a rel="nofollow ugc">http://www.11tmr.com/11tmr.nsf/emoticons/DLYH-5MZVLU/$FILE/wink.gif"</a>>.</p>

item.title: By: Simon
item.dc:creator: Simon
item.description: <p>Surely that can't be right? There are loads of Matthew White's out out there (which is not to say that you are not unique, <br/><br/>Matthew!). Fiona keeps telling me that we White's are a dime a dozen! </p>
